[CLS] [SEP] ( CNN)Boston native Mark Wahlberg will star in a film about the Boston Marathon bombing and the manhunt that followed , Deadline reported Wednesday . [CLS] [SEP] Wahlberg 's film , to be titled " Patriots ' Day , " is being produced by CBS Films , which linked to the Deadline article from its website . [CLS] [SEP] According to Deadline , Wahlberg is hoping to play Boston Police Commissioner Ed Davis , who retired after the attack in 2013 . [CLS] [SEP] The film will be told from Davis ' point of view . [CLS] [SEP] The film will feature material researched and shot by CBS Films ' corporate sibling , the CBS News program " 60 Minutes . [CLS] [SEP] " Wahlberg is also a producer of the film . [CLS] [SEP] " Patriots ' Day " is the second film related to the Boston bombing to be announced . [CLS] [SEP] Fox announced in November that it will be making a film called " Boston Strong " about the event .